想开发一个DamageSource，但编写@Override public ITextComponent getDeathMessage(EntityLivingBase)时发现不知道TextComponentTranslation的构造函数怎么用。super.getDeathMessage是这样写的：EntityLivingBase entitylivingbase = entityLivingBaseIn.getAttackingEntity();
String s = "death.attack." + this.damageType;
String s1 = s + ".player";
return entitylivingbase != null && I18n.canTranslate(s1) ? new TextComponentTranslation(s1, new Object[] {entityLivingBaseIn.getDisplayName(), entitylivingbase.getDisplayName()}) : new TextComponentTranslation(s, new Object[] {entityLivingBaseIn.getDisplayName()});
    复制代码求助new TextComponentTranslation用法。
